## BlueprintReadonlyGraph interface

Represents a blueprint graph of nodes with associated data.

Always has a single root node

**Signature:**

```typescript
export interface BlueprintReadonlyGraph<TData>
```

| [ancestorsByPriority(nodeId)](./models.blueprintreadonlygraph.ancestorsbypriority.md) | Get node ancestors by priority We are going bottom-to-top and by parent priority. Node grandparents are processed in order of priority of node's parents. This allows to handle complex use-cases with multiple parents on the same distance in different blueprint branches |
